{"tid":684623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴士司機按章工作　午間新聞　viutv：乘客齊贊成,別太累　tvb：不要阻人","createTime":"2018-05-30T16:40:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T16:42:22.000Z","uid":47714,"like":71,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c742d5716085148acdd929fc2300fed6412a8308","tid":684623,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:40:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1000042034734907397\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLungZenoOpen%2Fstatus%2F1000042034734907397&d=A9geYZzDo9425E11XSqJYKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=0b1d7f6c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLungZenoOpen%2Fstatus%2F1000042034734907397&h=6b1f582d\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1000042034734907397</a><br />\n<br />\n三個巴士工會按章工作爭取加薪減工時，viutv午間新聞（now午間新聞）報導，幾個候車乘客都是讚成，認為太累危險不應該，對比tvb午間新間，則篇幅短，提供一則說希望巴士不要阻礙。"},{"pid":"2390a99ba40e7b1516e6d489755b2566875d5fe7","tid":684623,"uid":29314,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:52:15.000Z","msg":"支支tvb就算鳩數啦"},{"pid":"920bbbe37babb28632f8c2cc656b57ba0f5296dd","tid":684623,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T17:51:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9a1d793bf6bb7dc73386c71d5dfc70cdc1999b8","tid":684623,"uid":176366,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T18:05:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/020508_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F020508_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=bc36e895&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"798cfe95f1d16c86571ab01873bf4e87015bcde8","tid":684623,"uid":126283,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T18:14:13.000Z","msg":"TVB啲新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇兩分鐘會覺得自己個鈍左<br />\n但啲廢中廢老睇得好開心<br />\n一邊同反支共既抵死，拉去坐監<br />\n又一邊真係覺得支那強大左，貿易戰又贏開巷<br />\n<br />\nTVB新聞最麻煩既地方係太方便，餵埋啲野入口，，又另外有新聞台，搞到啲人齋睇齋聽但唔撚識得分析，破綻百出又唔覺得有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我幫屋企del撚左新聞台又會變等睇六點半新聞，唔知以為睇得多會上癮"},{"pid":"c9580338e1bcc163fb329595b5130e2d2fb2bcd5","tid":684623,"uid":176366,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"798cfe95f1d16c86571ab01873bf4e87015bcde8","tid":684623,"uid":126283,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T18:14:13.000Z","msg":"TVB啲新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇兩分鐘會覺得自己個鈍左<br />\n但啲廢中廢老睇得好開心<br />\n一邊同反支共既抵死，拉去坐監<br />\n又一邊真係覺得支那強大左，貿易戰又贏開巷<br />\n<br />\nTVB新聞最麻煩既地方係太方便，餵埋啲野入口，，又另外有新聞台，搞到啲人齋睇齋聽但唔撚識得分析，破綻百出又唔覺得有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我幫屋企del撚左新聞台又會變等睇六點半新聞，唔知以為睇得多會上癮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T18:29:58.000Z","msg":"講得衰啲<br />\n好多香港人都鍾意速食 又不求甚解<br />\n<br />\n好似最近啲歐盟環保左膠 話香港人開冷氣開得太凍<br />\n就即刻聽曬人哋講 熄撚咗部冷氣 轉過撚頭熱到頂唔順又開返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開返又唔撚諗吓 點解要開咁多冷氣 下次俾人叫 又繼續loop<br />\n<br />\n講真<br />\n如果多少少人肯認真深入探討問題嘅 tvb呢啲垃圾新聞就畀人插到潛水啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9d1390cf202ee086ca2ab05b6f1ba35ae7aacd4","tid":684623,"uid":41245,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T18:59:48.000Z","msg":"廢中廢老立場嘛<br />\n根本本身佢地就係政治港孩<br />\n成個成長環境都俾英國寵壞晒<br />\n同你老母講啲新聞係假係偏頗嘅，佢地一定係會話「係咩～」「我唔識政治㗎～」，佢地根本就冇個sense去care自己接收嘅資訊"},{"pid":"f595078e69bccf46e6686cbbef68e267dc919e70","tid":684623,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl